    "question": "If Rs. 10000 amounts to Rs. 11664 invested in compound interest(compounded annually) for two years then the annual rate of compound interest is Rs.10000 2 덭撌 ￮뿚￿￿￪ 燐 (덭撌 헲 ) Rs. 11664 ￮뿚￿￿￪ 燐 덭撌 ?",
